{"tid":1364020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(哈哈哈) 劉業強：無法預料反對通知書會否引發更激烈衝突","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:05:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"024c2860a80eae00805635ea96920ddcc9fc30c5","tid":1364020,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/master_sandbox/2019/07/2019072516435993248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster_sandbox%2F2019%2F07%2F2019072516435993248.jpg&h=4892b983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗上周日有白衣人襲擊市民，造成45人受傷，有網民發起周六在元朗「光復元朗」遊行。不過警方發出反對通知書。鄉議局主席劉業強表示，相信警方已衡量過情況，有其理由反對；又指無法預料當日會否因為反對通知書而引發天激烈衝突。民主派議員則表示，若因為十八鄉鄉事委員會發出「一切嚴重後果由警方自負」的信件，便發出反對通知書，是製造白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n警方下午約4時發出反對通知書，適逢鄉議局主席劉業強及民主派議員正分別召開記者會回應遊行，傳媒當場詢問如何回應警方的反對通知書。劉業強指，相信警方克制冷靜，有收到意見時不希望在元朗有示威，擔心發生衝突。同時也有收到許多團體約見，冀表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，民主派議員鄺俊宇表示，稍後會向警方了解反對原因並要求解釋。郭家麒則指，《基本法》保證香港市民表達意見的自由，將了解警方理據，若開此先例的話是響起警號。郭續指，十八鄉鄉事委員會發出的信件涉嫌恐嚇，若警方因此「跪低」，是輕率決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/3636994/2019-07-25/news-%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E5%8A%89%E6%A5%AD%E5%BC%B7%EF%BC%9A%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E9%A0%90%E6%96%99%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E6%9B%B4%E6%BF%80%E7%83%88%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F3636994%2F2019-07-25%2Fnews-%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25BC%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%25BF%2580%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=1a67cce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/3636994/2019-07-25/news-%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E5%8A%89%E6%A5%AD%E5%BC%B7%EF%BC%9A%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E9%A0%90%E6%96%99%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E6%9B%B4%E6%BF%80%E7%83%88%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"bdfec342f8cd458db53886aab7b9ff9f26651353","tid":1364020,"uid":274526,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"其實劉業強唔妥何君妖㗎"},{"pid":"95ac945623520c60912bbc74eb50236e4ddb5828","tid":1364020,"uid":1315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:28:48.000Z","msg":"出反對 某程度迫更多人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通政府想我地收拾下d牛屎佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be8e5edb69e920b57bc8a4c8f45f3ae45ff2efc","tid":1364020,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"鄉村佬都分好多派"},{"pid":"c4997d233e9dc10843e1cf393fc04bfcce247917","tid":1364020,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2f58188d411e41a9f9bab028ba71f1602d8953","tid":1364020,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}